lester_mt2_bisect
=================

A fork of the code contained in Christopher G. Lester and Benjamin Nachman, _Bisection-based asymmetric MT2 computation: a higher precision calculator than existing symmetric methods_, [arXiv:1411.4312](http://arxiv.org/abs/1411.4312).

For the C wrapper, see [mt2_cwrapper](https://github.com/cbpark/mt2_cwrapper).

For an implementation in Haskell, see [hep-utilities](https://github.com/cbpark/hep-utilities/blob/master/src/HEP/Kinematics/Variable/MT2.hs).
